    <h1>TASTE OF SIN&#xAD;GA&#xAD;PORE CHOCO&#xAD;LATES</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200802/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-08-02"><time>2020-08-02</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE FOOD &amp; DRINK</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>What: Well-loved lo­cal flavours shine in a box of orchid-in­spired choco­late bon bons ($55 for a box of 16) by lo­cal pas­try chef Janice Wong.</p>
    <p>The eight flavours in­clude kopi, laksa leaf lemon­grass, gula me­laka pan­dan co­conut and kaf­fir lime salted caramel.</p>
    <p>For Na­tional Day ba­bies, or­der the choco­late gift set ($135) which also in­cludes a flower box of roses and or­chids from flo­ral bou­tique Fiore Do­rato.</p>
    <p>Where: Janice Wong Sin­ga­pore at B1-K28 Paragon, 290 Orchard Road</p>
    <p>When: Till Aug 12 Info: Or­der at www.jan­ice­wong. on­line for delivery</p>

